gtsoft.ivory.server.jca.cci
Interface IvoryRecord

All Known Implementing Classes:
IvoryBaseRecord, IvoryCallableServicesRecord, IvoryDomDocumentRecord, IvoryJDomDocumentRecord, IvoryStringRecord
public interface IvoryRecord

The IvoryRecord interface is implemented by all Ivory*Record classes. It guarantees classes using an IvoryRecord the getBytes and setBytes methods are available for use.
